==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nude
<hw>Nude</hw> <pr>(n⟦umac⟧d)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>nudus</ets>. See <er>Naked</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Bare;
naked; unclothed; undrapped; <as>as, a <ex>nude</ex>
statue</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>Naked; without consideration; void;
<as>as, a <ex>nude</ex> contract</as>. See <er>Nudum pactum</er>.</def>
<rj><au>Blackstone.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>The nude</b></col>, <cd>the undraped human figure in
art.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Nude"ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>- <wf>Nude"ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nudge</ent>⟦br⟧
